    <ul>
      <li>Multi-branch management</li>
      <li>Real-time Kitchen Display System</li>
      <li>QR ordering</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Visit your backoffice: <a href="https://{{subdomain}}.zayjar.com/backoffice">{{subdomain}}.zayjar.com/backoffice</a></p>
    <p>Need help? Reply to this email or check our docs.</p>
    <p>Best,<br>Zayjar Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
